sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant WhatsApp as WhatsApp App
    participant PaymentGateway as Payment Gateway
    participant Merchant as Merchant

    User->>WhatsApp: Initiates payment
    WhatsApp->>PaymentGateway: Request payment processing
    PaymentGateway-->>WhatsApp: Payment processing response
    WhatsApp->>Merchant: Notify payment success
    Merchant-->>User: Confirm payment received